name: We are all same in essence.
description:
"there are times.
more colorful, more beautiful,
brighter more pleasant,
but in the lens of reality
nothing lifted,
no dominant
bright or dark,
hot or cold,
because without one
it is difficult to appreciate the ability of another
just as the rainbow cannot be called a rainbow
if a single color is missing."

(may mga pagkakataong 
mas makulay, mas maganda
mas maliwanag mas kaaya-aya
pero sa lente ng reyalidad
walang nakaangat,
walang dominente
maliwanag o madilim,
mainit o malamig,
dahil kung wala ang isa 
mahirap pahalagahan ang kakayahan ng isa pa
gaya ng hindi masasabing bahaghari ang bahaghari
kung may iisang kulay nawawala.)
